** &quot;Polydactylus sextarius&quot; (Blackspot threadfin)
** &quot;Polydactylus siamensis&quot; (Largemouth striped threadfin)
** &quot;Polydactylus virginicus&quot; (Barbu)
* Genus &quot;Polynemus&quot;
** &quot;Polynemus aquilonaris&quot; (Northern paradise fish)
** &quot;Polynemus bidentatus&quot; 
